It gives a perfect balance of sweet and sour flavors. Ingredients Preparation Step 1 To make the syrup, Stir hot water and sugar together until the sugar is melted. Step 2 Using a shaker, add the mixture and then add all remaining ingredients and a few ice cubes. Step 3 Close the shaker tightly and shake well. Step 4 Add a few ice cubes into the martini glass plus the lemon twist. Step 5 Strain into a martini glass and enjoy